292
00:14:03,200 --> 00:14:05,505
You realize that that's more of a surprise
to anyone, right?

293
00:14:06,510 --> 00:14:08,575
I don't know. I just ended up there.

294
00:14:09,480 --> 00:14:10,975
Same here.

295
00:14:11,680 --> 00:14:14,105
Everyone is talking about how awkward
you two are with each other.

296
00:14:14,850 --> 00:14:16,019
I'm not cold.

297
00:14:16,020 --> 00:14:18,485
Your shirt keeps riding up when you dance.

298
00:14:20,320 --> 00:14:22,189
Woo-jae, the teacher is looking for you.

299
00:14:22,190 --> 00:14:23,285
Okay.

300
00:14:28,500 --> 00:14:30,259
How was he with Jae-yi earlier?

301
00:14:30,260 --> 00:14:33,425
Earlier? On the bus?

302
00:14:34,000 --> 00:14:35,439
It was quite the scene.

303
00:14:35,440 --> 00:14:37,635
I wish you could've seen their faces.

304
00:14:38,840 --> 00:14:41,175
Eun-taek, hold this.

305
00:14:41,480 --> 00:14:42,575
This?

306
00:14:44,180 --> 00:14:46,875
How can I get hot from dancing
in this weather?

307
00:14:47,820 --> 00:14:49,045
Are you serious?

308
00:14:49,820 --> 00:14:51,315
You don't have elastics on you, do you?

309
00:14:51,420 --> 00:14:52,515
You think I would?

310
00:14:53,950 --> 00:14:56,015
What about this?

311
00:14:56,520 --> 00:14:57,715
Would this help?

312
00:14:57,890 --> 00:15:00,589
How can I tie my hair with this?

313
00:15:00,590 --> 00:15:02,295
Why not? I think it'll work.

314
00:15:33,490 --> 00:15:35,295
How is it? Is it uncomfortable?

315
00:15:36,030 --> 00:15:37,865
It's not uncomfortable,

316
00:15:38,130 --> 00:15:39,395
