after the incident?

323
00:16:17,810 --> 00:16:20,309
Don't you feel like everything
just calmed down out of nowhere?

324
00:16:20,310 --> 00:16:22,405
Please give a round of applause
to Group Three.

325
00:16:24,850 --> 00:16:27,705
