on the field. ]

333
00:17:31,710 --> 00:17:33,549
I'll look for it. You can head inside.

334
00:17:33,550 --> 00:17:34,749
You're in Suite 304, right?

335
00:17:34,750 --> 00:17:36,845
Yes, sir. Thank you.

336
00:17:39,250 --> 00:17:41,319
Don't you think the guard is so handsome?

337
00:17:41,320 --> 00:17:42,555
Very.

338
00:17:42,920 --> 00:17:44,829
- Have you tried calling me?
- Yes.

339
00:17:44,830 --> 00:17:47,825
I told you that I tried calling
three times and nobody picked up.

340
00:17:48,730 --> 00:17:50,955
Miss, here.

341
00:17:51,370 --> 00:17:53,365
Your cellphone was on the ground.

342
00:17:53,400 --> 00:17:56,135
Really? What a relief!

343
00:17:56,470 --> 00:17:57,565
Please follow me.

344
00:17:58,340 --> 00:17:59,635
You two can go first.

345
00:18:01,540 --> 00:18:03,635
- Come here.
