- The red-headed girl.

348
00:18:07,280 --> 00:18:09,075
- When?
- Later.

349
00:18:15,860 --> 00:18:17,855
Let's go.

350
00:18:25,870 --> 00:18:27,025
My cap.

351
00:18:27,130 --> 00:18:28,639
Don't you think our guard is so handsome?

352
00:18:28,640 --> 00:18:30,799
He's really cute.

353
00:18:30,800 --> 00:18:33,139
Hey, is that yours?

354
00:18:33,140 --> 00:18:34,235
What did you say?

355
00:18:34,270 --> 00:18:35,775
Is that yours?

356
00:18:36,780 --> 00:18:39,145
It's Woo-jae's. He dropped it on the bus.

357
00:18:39,210 --> 00:18:42,019
Now that we're talking about it,
can you take it to Eun-taek tomorrow?

358
00:18:42,020 --> 00:18:43,179
Tell him that you picked it up.

359
00:18:43,180 --> 00:18:45,015
All right then.

360
00:18:46,150 --> 00:18:48,255
I saw Woo-jae

361
00:18:48,490 --> 00:18:50,755
smile at you big time earlier on.

362
00:18:50,790 --> 00:18:52,655
