363
00:18:52,930 --> 00:18:54,155
Woo-jae did?

364
00:18:54,230 --> 00:18:55,325
Yes.

365
00:18:55,800 --> 00:18:58,425
He was probably laughing
at how terrible I was.

366
00:18:59,200 --> 00:19:00,695
How are things going with you?

367
00:19:00,700 --> 00:19:02,469
What? What about me?

368
00:19:02,470 --> 00:19:04,569
You said that you've been talking
to some guy.

369
00:19:04,570 --> 00:19:07,305
Maybe a crush.

370
00:19:07,940 --> 00:19:10,639
- It's nothing like that.
- What do you mean?

371
00:19:10,640 --> 00:19:12,349
What school does he go to?
Where does he live?

372
00:19:12,350 --> 00:19:13,905
How often do you two talk to each other?

373
00:19:14,080 --> 00:19:15,019
Forget it.

374
00:19:15,020 --> 00:19:17,049
It's complicated already, so don't ask.

375
00:19:17,050 --> 00:19:18,619
If you like him, just date him.

376
00:19:18,620 --> 00:19:19,949
What more is there to think about?

377
00:19:19,950 --> 00:19:21,089
Don't overthink it.

378
00:19:21,090 --> 00:19:22,389
Just go for it. That's the answer.

379
00:19:22,390 --> 00:19:24,319
Hey, you shouldn't be the one talking.

380
00:19:24,320 --> 00:19:25,729
Hey, I...

381
00:19:25,730 --> 00:19:27,630
[ Lights are out in one minute. ]

