00:19:26,990 --> 00:19:31,665
[ Sky Forest School Retreat ]

383
00:19:31,870 --> 00:19:35,969
[ Do Woo-jae ]

384
00:19:35,970 --> 00:19:39,335
[ Thanks for everything up to now, Jae-yi. ]

385
00:19:39,810 --> 00:19:40,905
Are you crazy?

386
00:19:41,140 --> 00:19:43,010
- Who is it?
- Be quiet!

387
00:19:41,780 --> 00:19:42,905
[ Do Woo-jae ]

388
00:19:43,080 --> 00:19:44,705
Who just talked?

389
00:19:45,710 --> 00:19:49,075
My goodness. That scared me.

390
00:19:52,220 --> 00:19:53,915
[ Do Woo-jae is unavailable.
Press to redial. ]

391
00:19:54,150 --> 00:19:56,215
What do I do?

392
00:19:56,590 --> 00:19:58,285
What's wrong?

393
00:19:58,660 --> 00:20:01,055
What? It's nothing.

394
00:20:02,260 --> 00:20:04,700
[ Sorry. That was an accident. ]

395
00:20:02,860 --> 00:20:06,525
[ Sorry. That was an accident. ]

396
00:20:09,670 --> 00:20:10,995
[ Did you have something to say? ]

397
00:20:14,240 --> 00:20:20,610
[ Do Woo-jae ]

398
00:20:14,780 --> 00:20:17,275
[ Yes. You left your cap on the bus. ]

399
00:20:17,480 --> 00:20:18,745
[ I'll give it to you tomorrow. ]

400
00:20:20,680 --> 00:20:24,150
[ Do Woo-jae ]

401
00:20:20,750 --> 00:20:21,845
[ All right. ]

402
00:20:23,420 --> 00:20:25,545
What do I do? I'm an idiot!

403
00:20:26,720 --> 00:20:27,985
Are you serious?

404
00:20:27,990 --> 00:20:29,655
Hey, the bed is going to break!

405
00:20:32,490 --> 00:20:35,300
[ Do Woo-jae ]

406
00:20:32,860 --> 00:20:34,785
[ Would you like to give it to me
right now instead? ]

407
00:20:35,560 --> 00:20:36,655
No way!

408
00:20:38,030 --> 00:20:40,395
Hey, where did you leave the curling iron
earlier?

409
00:20:54,820 --> 00:20:56,720
[ I'll go there. You can wait for me. ]

410
00:20:54,820 --> 00:21:01,660
[ Do Woo-jae ]

411
00:20:56,780 --> 00:20:58,415
[ I'm already out. ]

412
00:20:58,520 --> 00:20:59,845
[ There are no guards. ]

413
00:21:02,890 --> 00:21:03,985
Goodness!

414
00:21:22,810 --> 00:21:24,375
I told you to just stay there.

415
00:21:40,730 --> 00:21:42,295
I don't think he's gone yet.

416
00:21:58,910 --> 00:22:00,045
Here you go.

417
00:22:01,310 --> 00:22:02,475
Thanks.

418
00:22:07,190 --> 00:22:10,985
Did you call me out here
at this hour for just a hat?

419
00:22:11,790 --> 00:22:14,055
- No.
- What?

420
00:22:17,760 --> 00:22:19,195
I missed you.

421
00:22:27,910 --> 00:22:29,775
I missed you, Jae-yi.

422
00:22:43,720 --> 00:22:45,255
[ Fire Door ]

423
00:22:47,190 --> 00:22:51,095
[ Sky Forest School Retreat ]

424
00:22:59,110 --> 00:23:01,809
- Hey, look at her face.
- What is that?

425
00:23:01,810 --> 00:23:04,039
I couldn't take that photo.
Send that one to me.

426
00:23:04,040 --> 00:23:06,475
- Send me the photo we took on the bus.
- Sure.

427
00:23:10,280 --> 00:23:12,219
[ Photos ]

428
00:23:12,220 --> 00:23:13,545
Really?

429
00:23:13,950 --> 00:23:16,119
- Oh, that?
- Goodness.

430
00:23:16,120 --> 00:23:17,220
I told you that.

431
00:23:16,120 --> 00:23:17,289
[ Photos ]

432
00:23:17,290 --> 00:23:20,390
[ Ji So-hyun ]

433
00:23:18,460 --> 00:23:20,025
[ Let's talk. ]

434
00:23:28,270 --> 00:23:29,795
Did you get your phone back?

435
00:23:40,380 --> 00:23:41,715
So-hyun.

436
00:23:42,480 --> 00:23:44,579
Well, are you the one who took my phone?

437
00:23:44,580 --> 00:23:45,615
Yes.

438
00:23:46,650 --> 00:23:48,185
I took it.

439
00:23:49,720 --> 00:23:50,759
Why?

440
00:23:50,760 --> 00:23:53,925
I needed to check something.
And I was right.

441
00:23:55,560 --> 00:23:56,895
It was you.

442
00:23:57,330 --> 00:23:59,225
The one who posted Ho-rang's photo.

443
00:24:00,670 --> 00:24:03,539
And the person who wrote stories
to provoke Ho-rang,

444
00:24:03,540 --> 00:24:05,509
who sent direct messages to Park Hye-rim,

445
00:24:05,510 --> 00:24:07,805
and who posted the photo online
during the festival

446
00:24:07,810 --> 00:24:09,135
was all you.

447
00:24:10,240 --> 00:24:12,745
Hey, So-hyun.

448
00:24:13,410 --> 00:24:15,319
You can't do that.

449
00:24:15,320 --> 00:24:17,145
Why did you go through my phone?

450
00:24:17,320 --> 00:24:18,245
Why?

451
00:24:18,890 --> 00:24:22,985
Did you think other people should live
a righteous life when you don't?

452
00:24:25,530 --> 00:24:27,029
Why did you do it?

453
00:24:27,030 --> 00:24:29,225
Didn't I tell you?

454
00:24:29,560 --> 00:24:32,365
She and I were classmates
in middle school.

455
00:24:33,070 --> 00:24:36,999
She couldn't even remember a classmate
who was in her class for a year.

456
00:24:37,000 --> 00:24:41,165
And she ignored me like I was some bug.
It was so annoying.

457
00:24:43,980 --> 00:24:45,649
So-hyun, I'm sure you know that too.

458
00:24:45,650 --> 00:24:48,945
Whenever she talks, she looks down
on people and patronizes them.

459
00:24:49,080 --> 00:24:52,215
She was a nobody like me
when she was in grade one.

460
00:24:52,290 --> 00:24:55,255
But she kept getting attention
when she didn't deserve it.

461
00:24:55,390 --> 00:24:56,819
She and I were on the same level,

462
00:24:56,820 --> 00:24:59,455
but it was ridiculous to see her
act all bossy like she was important.

463
00:24:59,530 --> 00:25:02,095
That's why I made it clear

464
00:25:02,160 --> 00:25:03,525
that she belonged

465
00:25:03,860 --> 00:25:07,025
here, on the bottom of the food chain,

466
00:25:07,600 --> 00:25:09,695
not all the way on top.

467
00:25:12,540 --> 00:25:13,635
Well,

468
00:25:14,110 --> 00:25:17,475
it was disappointing
when people thought she was the bully.

469
00:25:18,480 --> 00:25:20,805
- What do you mean?
- Right.

470
00:25:21,610 --> 00:25:25,075
She acted like she was all that
instead of learning her place.

471
00:25:25,820 --> 00:25:27,745
So she had it coming.

472
00:25:28,790 --> 00:25:29,985
"Had it coming?"

473
00:25:32,330 --> 00:25:33,585
So-hyun.

474
00:25:34,160 --> 00:25:35,959
Do you think all the posts I uploaded

475
00:25:35,960 --> 00:25:38,225
were all made up?

476
00:25:40,500 --> 00:25:41,865
Did you know?

477
00:25:42,600 --> 00:25:44,635
Actually, Baek Ho-rang

478
00:25:44,800 --> 00:25:46,765
doesn't like the number 16.

479
00:25:47,910 --> 00:25:49,375
Aren't you curious

480
00:25:49,640 --> 00:25:51,805
about what happened that day?

481
00:25:54,750 --> 00:25:57,745
School violence. Yes, that's it.

482
00:25:59,350 --> 00:26:01,285
That day, Ho-rang

483
00:26:02,460 --> 00:26:04,685
was beaten up by Lee Seon-ju.

484
00:26:15,340 --> 00:26:18,065
[ 2 years ago ]

485
00:26:37,360 --> 00:26:39,359
Happy birthday!

486
00:26:39,360 --> 00:26:42,559
Happy birthday. Happy birthday!

487
00:26:42,560 --> 00:26:44,655
- Who is she?
- A friend.

488
00:26:44,730 --> 00:26:45,895
She's my bestie.

489
00:26:46,330 --> 00:26:47,499
A bestie?

490
00:26:47,500 --> 00:26:49,369
I showed up. Now, that's it, right?

491
00:26:49,370 --> 00:26:50,639
I'll get going now.

492
00:26:50,640 --> 00:26:52,135
Where are you going?

493
00:26:52,770 --> 00:26:55,535
Are you trying to insult me
when I worked hard to set this up for you?

494
00:26:57,410 --> 00:26:58,575
Sit down.

495
00:26:59,950 --> 00:27:01,175
Let's have fun.

496
00:27:01,250 --> 00:27:02,745
Let's have a blast.

497
00:27:02,850 --> 00:27:04,175
Ta-da.

498
00:27:05,220 --> 00:27:08,185
- This is crazy.
- Who would wear something like that?

499
00:27:08,960 --> 00:27:10,389
Put it on her now.

500
00:27:10,390 --> 00:27:11,929
My goodness.

501
00:27:11,930 --> 00:27:15,929
- My gosh, that's so cute.
- So cute.

502
00:27:15,930 --> 00:27:19,599
Ho-rang, you're an elephant.
You should spin like this.

503
00:27:19,600 --> 00:27:21,595
Where's Room Seven?

504
00:27:25,540 --> 00:27:27,035
- No way.
- It looks good on you.

505
00:27:29,110 --> 00:27:31,279
- Nice.
- Spin.

506
00:27:31,280 --> 00:27:34,305
- It looks good on you.
- Gosh.

507
00:27:47,690 --> 00:27:49,595
I think she smells.

508
00:27:50,400 --> 00:27:52,625
Hey, I have perfume. Wait.

509
00:27:52,730 --> 00:27:55,565
- It's expensive. Don't use it too much.
- Okay.

510
00:27:59,040 --> 00:28:01,935
- Hey.
