01:00:09,430 --> 01:00:12,435
but how could I do that?

1037
01:00:14,670 --> 01:00:17,505
You're still a friend to me.

1038
01:00:23,480 --> 01:00:24,645
Don't you feel that way too?

1039
01:00:26,580 --> 01:00:27,785
Hey, Ji So-hyun.

1040
01:00:30,220 --> 01:00:31,515
Don't overreact.

1041
01:00:33,420 --> 01:00:34,625
You and I

1042
01:00:38,430 --> 01:00:40,825
stopped being friends two years ago.

1043
01:00:44,400 --> 01:00:46,869
Ho-rang. Baek Ho-rang.

1044
01:00:46,870 --> 01:00:49,065
Please.

1045
01:00:49,310 --> 01:00:51,805
Please.

1046
01:01:06,990 --> 01:01:09,155
This is why I don't like you.

1047
01:01:10,900 --> 01:01:14,095
I'm so embarrassed.
How can I see you again?

1048
01:01:18,040 --> 01:01:19,295
Let's not

1049
01:01:21,840 --> 01:01:23,765
cross paths anymore.

1050
01:02:46,697 --> 01:02:49,892
[ Live On ]

1051
01:02:49,994 --> 01:02:52,093
- Are you crazy?
- You must be really scared.

1052
01:02:52,094 --> 01:02:52,993
Hey, Jeong Hui-su.

1053
01:02:52,994 --> 01:02:55,333
Quit the broadcasting team.

1054
01:02:55,334 --> 01:02:56,733
[ What did you say to Baek Ho-rang? ]

1055
01:02:56,734 --> 01:02:58,133
[ I'm quitting the broadcasting team. ]

1056
01:02:58,134 --> 01:03:00,633
Eun-taek. I'll tell you everything.

1057
01:03:00,634 --> 01:03:02,733
[ It's something Baek Ho-rang
will never tell you. ]

1058
01:03:02,734 --> 01:03:04,073
Say something before you leave.

1059
01:03:04,074 --> 01:03:06,373
Everything in that post is true.

1060
01:03:06,374 --> 01:03:08,009
[ Your expression
is a sight for sore eyes. ]

1061
01:03:08,314 --> 01:03:10,343
[ Is that all you can say ]

1062
01:03:10,344 --> 01:03:12,209
[ to someone who has been waiting for you? ]

1063
01:03:12,314 --> 01:03:14,179
[ I'm regretting telling you ]

1064
01:03:14,254 --> 01:03:16,379
[ that I like you for the first time. ]

1065
01:03:19,550 --> 01:03:22,979
[ Epilogue ]

1066
01:03:22,980 --> 01:03:25,149
- Hey, that's her.
- Who?

1067
01:03:25,150 --> 01:03:26,879
The girl who dates a bunch of guys.

1068
01:03:26,880 --> 01:03:29,019
- That's crazy. Are you serious?
- Yes.

1069
01:03:29,020 --> 01:03:31,115
- That's her.
- No way.

1070
01:03:31,850 --> 01:03:33,045
Hey.

1071
01:03:33,620 --> 01:03:36,315
Do you have a lip tint on you?

1072
01:03:36,390 --> 01:03:37,355
What? Yes.

1073
01:03:38,690 --> 01:03:39,855
Here.

1074
01:03:41,860 --> 01:03:43,725
Do you have a different color?

1075
01:03:47,030 --> 01:03:48,435
What about this one?

1076
01:03:51,010 --> 01:03:52,839
You only have guy friends, right?

1077
01:03:52,840 --> 01:03:54,839
- What?
- That's what I heard.

1078
01:03:54,840 --> 01:03:57,705
I heard you don't have any girl friends,
and you only hang out with guys.

1079
01:03:58,150 --> 01:04:00,675
Oh, right. The thing is...

1080
01:04:01,320 --> 01:04:04,049
I'm more comfortable talking to guys,

1081
01:04:04,050 --> 01:04:07,815
but that doesn't mean I feel uncomfortable
talking to girls.

1082
01:04:08,360 --> 01:04:10,415
Why are you making excuses?

1083
01:04:10,830 --> 01:04:12,325
That's how people are.

1084
01:04:12,390 --> 01:04:15,925
When someone is different from them,
they think that they're weird.

1085
01:04:16,800 --> 01:04:18,899
- Are you dating all of them?
- No!

1086
01:04:18,900 --> 01:04:22,565
Then it's not weird that
you have a lot of guy friends.

1087
01:04:23,800 --> 01:04:24,965
But

1088
01:04:25,470 --> 01:04:27,269
this color is definitely weird.

1089
01:04:27,270 --> 01:04:29,105
Nobody would use this.

1090
01:04:30,510 --> 01:04:32,275
Is it that bad?

1091
01:04:40,050 --> 01:04:41,085
Hey.

1092
01:04:41,420 --> 01:04:42,885
Hey, then

1093
01:04:45,830 --> 01:04:47,995
can you come with me to buy some later?

1094
01:04:51,470 --> 01:04:54,469
Or you can just tell me
what's a good one to buy.

1095
01:04:54,470 --> 01:04:56,465
I'm going to buy a cushion compact
after school.

1096
01:04:57,510 --> 01:04:58,805
You can come with me if you want.

1097
01:05:01,910 --> 01:05:02,935
Okay.

1098
01:05:08,350 --> 01:05:10,575
Hey, are you a good student?

1099
01:05:10,820 --> 01:05:13,350
- Kind of.
- Gosh, you're so annoying.

1100
01:05:10,820 --> 01:05:14,589
[ Ji So-hyun, Baek Ho-rang ]

1101
01:05:14,590 --> 01:05:19,385
[ Ji So-hyun, Baek Ho-rang ]

